other_tests.findings: Proliferative endometrium and fragments of benign endocervix.
Solid, hypoechoic pelvic mass anterior to the uterus, measuring 9.9 cm in greatest diameter, with a moderate volume of free fluid and a small simple cyst in the left ovary.
Right ovarian mass (11.5 cm by 8.5 cm by 7.8 cm) diagnosed as an ovarian fibroma.
